headline: FIS to Present at Upcoming Conference
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., June 09, 2025--FIS® (NYSE: FIS), a global leader in financial technology, will present on Tuesday, June 10, 2025, at the Mizuho Technology Conference at 3:35pm ET.
